### =====================================================================
### ApiLog API  (base route: api/ApiLog/)
### TagApiLog: 101 Get,102 Post,... 201 Success,202 ClientError,203 ServerError,301 HasException
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Read - all
POST {{host}}/api/ApiLog/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "pageSize": 50,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "orderBy": 118,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### Read - only errors + slow requests
POST {{host}}/api/ApiLog/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "onlyErrors": true,
  "minDurationMs": 1000,
  "pathContains": "/api/product/",
  "pageSize": 50,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### Read - by status code + trace
POST {{host}}/api/ApiLog/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "statusCode": 500,
  "pageSize": 20,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### Stats - hourly buckets
POST {{host}}/api/ApiLog/Stats
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "fromCreatedAt": "2026-07-01T00:00:00Z",
  "toCreatedAt": "2026-07-05T00:00:00Z",
  "bucket": "hour"
}

### Stats - daily buckets
POST {{host}}/api/ApiLog/Stats
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "bucket": "day"
}

### Export (returns a CSV file)
POST {{host}}/api/ApiLog/Export
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "onlyErrors": false,
  "pageSize": 1000,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}
